e avatar&rsquo;s base attack bonus. An avatar&rsquo;s base attack bonus is equal to its Hit Dice. Avatars do not gain additional attacks using their natural weapons for a high base attack bonus.</p>\n<p>Fort/Ref/Will:&nbsp;These are the avatar&rsquo;s base saving throw bonuses. An avatar has good Reflex and Will saves.</p>\n<p>Skills:&nbsp;This lists the avatar&rsquo;s total skill ranks. An avatar can assign skill ranks to any skill. Avatars with Intelligence scores above the base value modify these totals as normal. An avatar cannot have more ranks in a skill than it has Hit Dice. Avatar skill ranks are set once chosen.</p>\n<p>The following skills are class skills for avatars: Bluff (Cha), Craft (Int), Knowledge (planes) (Int), Perception (Wis), Sense Motive (Wis), and Stealth (Dex). In addition, at 1st level, the summoner can choose 4 additional skills to be class skills for his avatar. Note that avatars with a fly speed receive Fly (Dex) as a free class skill.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[]},"tag":"avatarClassHd","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"classType":"racial","classSubType":"none","parentClass":"Summoner","levels":{"value":0,"_deprecated":true},"level":1,"lvl":0,"countforexp":"exp","hd":10,"hp":10,"classCastingStat":"noncaster","classBaseMPTypes":"noncaster","classBaseMPauto":"no","mp":0,"bab":"high","skillsPerLevel":4,"savingThrows":{"fort":{"value":"low"},"ref":{"value":"high"},"will":{"value":"high"}},"fc":{"hp":{"value":0},"skill":{"value":0},"alt":{"value":0}},"classSkills":{"acr":false,"apr":false,"blf":true,"clm":false,"crf":true,"dip":false,"dev":false,"dis":false,"dri":false,"esc":false,"fly":false,"han":false,"hea":false,"int":false,"kar":false,"kd